.PP
.if n *
.if t \(bu
Cook has been ported to Windows-NT using CygWin32.
See the BUILDING file for details.
.PP
.if n *
.if t \(bu
There are two new functions (\fIdos-path\fP and \fIun-dos-path\fP)
for use when invoking non-CygWin32 WindowsNT programs.
See the Cook User Guide for more information.
.PP
.if n *
.if t \(bu
Fingerprints now work meaningfully with directories.
.PP
.if n *
.if t \(bu
A bug has been fixed in the pattern matching code.
It would sometimes cause core dumps.
.PP
.if n *
.if t \(bu
A bug involving fingerprints in combination with the search_list has
been fixed.  Cook would occasionally conclude that a shallow target was
up-to-date when a shallow ingredient was edited to be the same as a
deeper ingredient.
.PP
.if n *
.if t \(bu
A bug has been fixed in cooktime.
It would use an inappropriate timezone offset on some systems.
.\" ---------------------- Add New Notes Above This Line ------------------
.SS "Release 2.5 (1998-Sep-02)"
